history.content: Its definitely doable but expect to have a semester with a very high and constant workload. 106B is almost 2x the workload of 106A and 110 can be hard depending on the professor teaching. I would advise you to take a lighter third tech as with this schedule, I feel that it would be hard to make the most out of a class like 189.

children.subject: Can you put off EECS 106B?  Math 110 is a great accompaniment to CS 189.
